"title": "5875: hatred",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5875: hatred",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Hatred for others or God is associated with human sin. Scripture also emphasises God's hatred of sin and evil. Believers are commanded to love those who hate them.</p>\n<h2>Hatred as evidence of corrupt human nature</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:15\">2SA 13:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:3\">TIT 3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:4\">GEN 37:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:15\">DEU 7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:11-Deut19:12\">DEU 19:11–19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:7\">JDG 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:22\">2SA 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:19\">PSA 25:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:19\">PSA 38:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:12\">PRO 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:10\">MAT 24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:20\">GAL 5:19–5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:9-1John2:11\">1JN 2:9–2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:15\">1JN 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:20\">1JN 4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Hatred of God himself</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:15\">PSA 81:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:29-Rom1:31\">ROM 1:29–1:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:5\">EXO 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:10\">DEU 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:41\">DEU 32:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:2\">2CH 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:17\">PSA 50:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:29\">PRO 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:20\">JHN 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:23-John15:25\">JHN 15:23–15:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a></p>\n<h2>Hatred of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:7\">JHN 7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">ISA 53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:14\">MAT 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:46\">MAT 21:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:3-Matt26:4\">MAT 26:3–26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:22\">MAT 27:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:14\">LUK 19:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a></p>\n<h2>Hatred of the godly and upright</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:8\">1KI 22:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:22\">MAT 10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:1\">EST 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:19\">PSA 35:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:4\">PSA 69:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:3-Ps109:5\">PSA 109:3–109:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:10\">PRO 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:5\">ISA 66:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:10\">AMO 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:9-Matt24:10\">MAT 24:9–24:10</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:13\">MRK 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:16-Luke21:19\">LUK 21:16–21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:69-Luke1:71\">LUK 1:69–1:71</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:22\">LUK 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18\">JHN 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:29\">ACT 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:12-Acts23:15\">ACT 23:12–23:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to love those who hate them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:28\">LUK 6:27–6:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:44\">MAT 5:43–5:44</a></p>\n<h2>God's hatred of evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:4-Ps5:5\">PSA 5:4–5:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:16-Prov6:19\">PRO 6:16–6:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:8\">ISA 61:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:31\">DEU 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:21-Deut16:22\">DEU 16:21–16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:5\">PSA 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:14\">ISA 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:8\">JER 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:15\">HOS 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21\">AMO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:16\">MAL 2:16</a></p>\n<h2>The godly should also hate evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">PRO 8:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9\">ROM 12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:21\">EXO 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:6\">PSA 31:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:10\">PSA 97:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:3\">PSA 101:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:104\">PSA 119:104</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:113\">PSA 119:113</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:128\">PSA 119:128</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:163\">PSA 119:163</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:21\">PSA 139:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:5\">PRO 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:17\">PRO 15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:15\">AMO 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:9\">HEB 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:7\">PSA 45:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:6\">REV 2:6</a></p>",
